{"tid":2307113,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"四名法國警察因「暴力執法」被起訴 其中兩人已還押候審","createTime":"2020-12-01T03:16:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-01T04:40:45.000Z","uid":240362,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ec2863db0cb4c3bf08169b72caaf9f6ffb8dd638","tid":2307113,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T03:16:40.000Z","msg":"法國四名警察因涉毆打非裔音樂製作人澤克勒（Michel Zecler），已遭刑事調查。媒體週一援引司法人員消息指，四名涉事警察面臨「暴力執法」指控，其中兩人已還押候審。<br />\n<br />\n11月21日，澤克勒在其位於巴黎的工作室內遭三名警察踢打，暴力持續數分鐘。上週四，Loopsider網站公布了監控拍到的施暴畫面。馬克龍週五對警察暴力提出強烈譴責，並要求落實涉事警察責任。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-55127815\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-55127815&d=3wrM%2FJom4zLweqSprMIx0pwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=6378e5f7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-55127815&h=1eb139d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-55127815</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://theinitium.com/article/20201201-morning-brief/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheinitium.com%2Farticle%2F20201201-morning-brief%2F&d=3wrM%2FJom4zLweqSprMIx0pwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=27797626\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://theinitium.com/article/20201201-morning-brief/</a>"},{"pid":"2e5890625ac1c34ffb2e2eb619632aec0337eec0","tid":2307113,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T03:16:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"953ba8c8af4f2340d80e1822a87e8c8e3cbf9cae","tid":2307113,"uid":141668,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T03:17:28.000Z","msg":"藍屍：喺外國警察一早開咗槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e898da1327ea1d414df6143f6f72f6db892daec0","tid":2307113,"uid":121197,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T03:23:19.000Z","msg":"藍絲：警察無罪，黃屍